Rule File Pathname: /home/user1/Desktop/ic/_SMIC_CalDRC_018LGMS_1833_V1.19_REV1_0.drc_
Slot density of wide metal >=1.5% when
1. The wide metal is > 35*35 um. DRC checks the metal main pattern(61:0, 62:0ż), not following (Mn-MnSLOT).
2. The wide metal interacts with metal slot (61:2, 62:2...)
3. Metal slot (61:2, 62:2ż) size > 10*10 um are not included this rule density calculation.
4. DRC doesn't check metals interact with PA.
5. DRC individually exports result by each metal layer.
